<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <!-- SEO Optimization -->
  <title>Convert Text to Uppercase - Online Text Converter</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Convert text to uppercase instantly with our free online tool.  A simple and efficient way to transform lowercase text to uppercase.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="uppercase, lowercase, text converter, convert to uppercase, convert to lowercase, text transformation, online text tool, string manipulation">
  <meta name="author" content="SOFTICA">

  <!-- Open Graph -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="Uppercase Converter">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Easily convert text to uppercase with this simple online tool.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://util-tool-online.com/to-uppercase"> <!-- Update with your actual URL -->
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://util-tool-online.com/images/util-tool-online.png"> <!-- Update with your image URL -->

  <!-- Twitter Cards -->
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="https://util-tool-online.com/images/util-tool-online.png">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Uppercase Converter">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Convert lowercase text to uppercase quickly and easily.">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://util-tool-online.com/images/util-tool-online.png"> <!-- Update with your image URL -->

  <!-- Styles -->
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
      <!-- Left Menu -->
      <div class="col-md-2">
        <%- include('partials/left-menu') %>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="col-md-10">
        <h1>Text to Uppercase Converter</h1>
        <p>This tool converts lowercase letters in your text to uppercase. It's a quick and easy way to standardize text case.</p>

        <!-- Usage Instructions -->
        <section class="mt-4">
          <h2>How to Use</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>Enter your text in the input field below.</li>
            <li>Click the "Convert to Uppercase" button.</li>
            <li>The uppercase version of your text will appear in the result section.</li>
            <li>Click "Copy to Clipboard" to copy the result.</li>
            <li>Click "Clear" to reset the input and output fields.</li>
          </ol>
        </section>

        <!-- Input Section -->
        <section class="mt-5">
          <h2>Enter Text</h2>
          <form id="uppercase-form" action="/to-uppercase" method="POST">
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="text" class="form-label">Enter Text</label>
              <textarea class="form-control" id="text" name="text" rows="6" required><%= text || '' %></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Convert to Uppercase</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" id="clear-btn">Clear</button>
          </form>
        </section>

        <!-- Result Section -->
        <% if (result) { %>
        <section class="mt-5">
          <h2>Result</h2>
          <pre class="bg-light p-3 rounded" id="result"><%= result %></pre>
          <button class="btn btn-success mt-2" id="copy-btn">Copy to Clipboard</button>
        </section>
        <% } %>

        <!-- About Uppercase Conversion -->
        <section class="mt-5">
          <h2>About Uppercase Conversion</h2>
          <p>Converting text to uppercase involves changing all lowercase letters in a string to their uppercase equivalents. This is a common text manipulation task used in various applications, including:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Data Standardization:</strong> Ensuring consistency in data sets where case sensitivity might cause issues.</li>
            <li><strong>Programming:</strong>  Often used in programming tasks to compare strings without case sensitivity.</li>
            <li><strong>Text Processing:</strong> As part of larger text processing pipelines for tasks like searching or sorting.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Advantages</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> Straightforward transformation.</li>
            <li><strong>Consistency:</strong> Ensures uniform case across text.</li>
            <li><strong>Case-Insensitive Comparisons:</strong> Useful for comparisons where case doesn't matter.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Disadvantages</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Loss of Information:</strong>  Original case is lost.</li>
            <li><strong>Readability:</strong>  All uppercase text can be less readable than mixed-case text.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Examples</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Input: "hello world" Output: "HELLO WORLD"</li>
            <li>Input: "This Is A Sentence." Output: "THIS IS A SENTENCE."</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Clear and Copy Script -->
        <script>
          document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const clearBtn = document.getElementById('clear-btn');
            const textArea = document.getElementById('text');
            const resultArea = document.getElementById('result');
            const copyBtn = document.getElementById('copy-btn');

            clearBtn?.addEventListener('click', () => {
              textArea.value = '';
              resultArea.textContent = '';
            });

            copyBtn?.addEventListener('click', () => {
              navigator.clipboard.writeText(resultArea.textContent)
                .then(() => alert('Result copied to clipboard!'))
                .catch(err => console.error('Copy failed:', err));
            });
          });
        </script>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
